# ChangeLog for priss

## v5.0.3

 * allow incarnations to work on original formula, then does not participate in sharing (both send and receive)
 * set LBD value of received clauses based on size, or average LBD/size ratio
 * pfolio can pass configurations from commandline to each incarnation with extra semantic [N]configN[N+1]configN+1, can also pass options to all incarnations
 * use extra buffer to share multiunits and equivalences
 * enabled incranations to perform vivification on received clauses, and to sent shrinked clauses again
 * have global simplifier for pfolio
 * use pfolioconfig object to setup configurations
 * can share equivalence classes and sets of unit clauses
